<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal"
      xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
      xmlns:i18n="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/i18n"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/main_template/macros/master"
      i18n:domain="vindula.content">

<body>
<metal:main fill-slot="content-core">
 	<metal:content-core define-macro="content-core">
			<div class="topoBox_colunaTotal">
				<div class="info_topoBoxTipo">
					<div class="info_data">
						<h4 tal:content="python: context.effective_date.strftime('%d/%m/%Y / %H:%m')"></h4>
					</div>
					<!--div class="indicacao_comentario">
						<h4>Comentário (3)</h4>
					</div-->
					<div class="visualClear"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="geral_contBox">
				<div class="contBox_colunaTotal">
					<div class="info"> 
						<div class="titulo_info">
							<h2 tal:content="context/Title"></h2>
							<div class="descricao_titulo">
								<h4 tal:content="python: 'Autor: %s' % context.getOwner().getUserName()"></h4>
								<p tal:content="context/summary"></p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<!-- viewlet compartilhar -->
						
						<div class="img_descricao">
							<div class="img_info">
								<div class="bk_topo_imgDestaque">
									<img alt="" src="++theme++vindula.themedefault/images/bk_topo_imgDestaque.png"/>
								</div>
								<div class="bk_cont_imgDestaque">
									<img alt="" width="156" tal:attributes="src string:${context/image/to_object/absolute_url}/image_mini;
																alt context/imageCaption; title context/imageCaption;"/>
								</div>
								<div class="bk_rodape_imgDestaque">
									<img alt="" src="++theme++vindula.themedefault/images/bk_rodape_imgDestaque.png"/>
								</div>
							</div>							
							
							<div class="descricao_destaque texto_pagina" tal:content="structure context/text/output">
								
							</div>
							<div class="visualClear"></div>
						</div>
						<!-- viewlet compartilhar -->
	
					</div>
					
					<div class="geral_lista_comentarios">
						<div class="titulo_area">
							<h2>Comentários (3)</h2>
						</div>
						<div class="descricao_titulo">
							<p>Donec nec elit ut nunc blandit convallis. Nullam quis odio eget erat tempus imperdiet et a est.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="bt_comentar">
							<input type="submit" value="Comentar" class="">
						</div>
						<div class="lista_comentarios">
							<div class="item_lista">
								<h4><span>José da Silva</span><span> | </span>09/11/2011 - 14h12</h4>
								<p>Donec nec elit ut nunc blandit convallis. Nullam quis odio eget erat tempus imperdiet et a est. Suspendisse quis dolor vitae arcu sagittis ultricies a et felis. Vestibulum eu dui eget erat semper commodo. Curabitur eu nisl eu ipsum varius consequat id quis leo.</p>
							</div>
							<div class="item_lista">
								<h4><span>Maria do Socorro</span><span> | </span>09/11/2011 - 14h12</h4>
								<p>Blandit convallis. Vestibulum eu dui eget erat semper commodo. Curabitur eu nisl eu ipsum varius consequat id quis leo. Nullam quis odio eget erat tempus imperdiet et a est. Suspendisse quis dolor vitae arcu sagittis ultricies a et felis..</p>
							</div>
							<div class="item_lista borderBottomNone paddingNone">
								<h4><span>Pedro Miranda</span><span> | </span>09/11/2011 - 14h12</h4>
								<p>Donec nec elit ut nunc blandit convallis. Nullam quis odio eget erat tempus imperdiet et a est. Suspendisse quis dolor vitae arcu sagittis ultricies a et felis.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
					
					
				
			</div>
	</metal:content-core>
</metal:main>
</body>
</html>